    <i class="icon-localcloud gigantic dark_red"></i>
    <h5>Combine local and cloud integrations</h5>
    <p class="small-text">Integrate whatever you want, be it <strong>cloud</strong> based applications and datasources, or your own database/application in your <strong>private</strong>/local network. </p>
  </div>
</div>
<div class="row centered-text">
